          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The system takes significant steps to reduce thermal state. Fans are running at maximum speed."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Reduce usage of the CPU, GPU, and I/O such as Bluetooth or network to the minimum level required for user interaction. If possible, stop using peripherals such as the camera, flash, microphone, and speaker."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
